snippet.textDisplay:
This has been around at least since December 19th, but the press coverage was geared to covering the impeachment hearings. Covid - 19 appears to present differently than the common cold which is also a coronavirus (FACT). It appears to affect the respiratory system and presents in a CT scan differently way than pneumonia. It seems the course of the illness is about 10-17 days and yes like most common colds, you can get it again. The death rate for the flu is about 0.1 percent; you probably will see similar statistics for Covid - 19. Most people dying will probably have an impaired immune system or respiratory system; again senior citizens, infants, auto immune disease. It does not matter if there are 2 cases or 100,000 cases; even case will be isolated, people treating the infected person will wear protective clothing. The CDC will test as many people as necessary, and people will have CT scans along with anti-virals, plenty of liquids and if needed incubation to help them breathe and at last resort steroids. Best practice wash you hands and do touch your mouth.

The vast majority of people who contract the virus experience only mild, cold-like symptoms and community spread cases could be people who have not been properly interviewed or they are not telling the truth about their exposure. Anything beyond this is probably not true and is speculation. Such an event should not be used for political purposes. The Federal government has enough funding to last until April (FACT). The flu season usually lasts until April.
